	<ThingDef ParentName="FightSystem_LightHammer">
		<defName>DankPyon_MeleeWeapon_Pickaxe</defName>
		<label>pickaxe</label>
		<description>A mining tool used to batter stones and ingots; although primarily used to gather economic resources, the mine features deadly picks at both ends, capable of decimating armor as effectively as it mines ore.</description>
